title: DC Comics July 2014 Bombshell Covers
description:
This is the complete collection of the Bombshell Variant Covers, that DC Comics released during the month of July 2014. These are scans of my collection and all scans are in HD. This is my first time scanning and my first time uploading so any advice would be appreciated. The covers in this collection are:

-Action Comics #32
-Aquaman #32
-Batgirl #32
-Batman #32
-Batman and Ra's Al Ghul #32
-Batman-Superman #32
-Batwoman #32
-Catwoman #32
-Detective Comics #32
-Earth 2 #24
-Flash #32
-Green Lantern #32
-Green Lantern Corps #32
-Harley Quinn #7
-Justice League #32
-Justice League Dark #32
-Justice League United #2
-Red Hood and the Outlaws #32
-Superman #32
-Superman-Wonder Woman #9
-Wonder Woman #32
